<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٦٠٣ - وَقَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1056">ثَابِتٌ </a>: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6092">مِسْعَرٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5419">مُحَارِبٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1091">جَابِرٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span>: <span class="c2">«أَتَيْتُ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> فِي الْمَسْجِدِ، فَقَضَانِي وَزَادَنِي.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>